00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:09,970
we won't call you heartless.

572
00:38:11,700 --> 00:38:13,010
That's human nature.

573
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:20,680
When you reach our age,

574
00:38:21,540 --> 00:38:22,640
you'll understand.

575
00:38:23,430 --> 00:38:24,270
You

576
00:38:25,100 --> 00:38:26,840
can't fight genetics.

577
00:38:28,100 --> 00:38:30,130
You can't fight human nature.

578
00:38:30,580 --> 00:38:33,160
You can't fight fate.

579
00:38:39,870 --> 00:38:40,890
These years,

580
00:38:41,830 --> 00:38:42,930
you've had it tough,

581
00:38:44,750 --> 00:38:46,030
taking care of us

582
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:47,130
and the kid.

583
00:38:49,540 --> 00:38:50,530
Thank you.

584
00:38:58,750 --> 00:39:01,240
Live the life you want.

585
00:39:01,910 --> 00:39:02,840
Don't overthink it.

586
00:39:04,180 --> 00:39:05,610
Don't be too responsible.

587
00:39:07,270 --> 00:39:09,320
In this life, to put it plainly,

588
00:39:09,540 --> 00:39:11,410
there are only so many decades.

589
00:39:12,270 --> 00:39:15,870
If the happy times outnumber the tough times,

590
00:39:15,870 --> 00:39:17,130
then your life

591
00:39:17,470 --> 00:39:18,310
is worth it.

592
00:39:28,750 --> 00:39:29,590
Don't be sad.

593
00:39:36,430 --> 00:39:37,720
Honestly,

594
00:39:39,220 --> 00:39:42,840
I miss you being a kid.

595
00:39:44,100 --> 00:39:45,410
So carefree.

596
00:39:54,060 --> 00:39:54,930
Take care of yourself.

597
00:39:55,220 --> 00:39:56,450
There's still a long road ahead.

598
00:39:59,180 --> 00:40:00,240
I believe in you.

599
00:40:05,540 --> 00:40:07,350
Are you Cupid?

600
00:40:07,350 --> 00:40:08,840
What right do you have to oppose?

601
00:40:09,060 --> 00:40:11,360
She's my sister, or I won't meddle.

602
00:40:11,580 --> 00:40:13,700
It's not like high blood pressure or diabetes,

603
00:40:13,700 --> 00:40:15,640
