with injections and medicine.

604
00:40:15,910 --> 00:40:17,310
That's a life-threatening illness.

605
00:40:17,310 --> 00:40:18,390
To put it bluntly,

606
00:40:18,390 --> 00:40:19,530
you never know when he might...

607
00:40:21,060 --> 00:40:22,130
Die?

