616
00:40:38,830 --> 00:40:39,680
What's the point?

617
00:40:40,020 --> 00:40:42,310
Everyone is born heading towards death.

618
00:40:42,310 --> 00:40:43,150
Shall we die anyway?

619
00:40:45,500 --> 00:40:46,890
I understand this reasoning.

620
00:40:47,270 --> 00:40:49,180
I just can't get over it.

621
00:40:49,180 --> 00:40:51,060
Why do you need to get over it?

622
00:40:51,060 --> 00:40:52,740
That's Rose's job.

623
00:40:52,740 --> 00:40:54,450
You need to leave it to her.

624
00:40:55,580 --> 00:40:56,420
Well.

625
00:40:56,540 --> 00:40:59,360
The psychologist made you broad-minded.

626
00:41:01,100 --> 00:41:02,020
Do you know?

627
00:41:02,020 --> 00:41:03,830
The day you went to see the psychologist,

628
00:41:03,830 --> 00:41:05,610
I was there officiating a wedding.

629
00:41:06,060 --> 00:41:07,970
I couldn't even concentrate properly.

630
00:41:08,790 --> 00:41:11,450
What did the psychologist tell you?

631
00:41:15,660 --> 00:41:17,130
My psychologist said

632
00:41:17,470 --> 00:41:20,240
