633
00:41:22,660 --> 00:41:24,240
Keeping a secret from me, huh?

634
00:42:04,270 --> 00:42:05,110
Listen.

635
00:42:09,430 --> 00:42:10,840
The guy outside,

636
00:42:11,540 --> 00:42:13,490
