637
00:42:15,100 --> 00:42:15,940
Snore.

638
00:42:16,060 --> 00:42:16,900
Breathe.

639
00:42:17,270 --> 00:42:18,110
Snore.

640
00:42:18,270 --> 00:42:19,110
Breathe.

641
00:42:20,310 --> 00:42:21,360
The one inside

642
00:42:21,620 --> 00:42:22,680
is in 3/4 time.

643
00:42:23,700 --> 00:42:26,530
Snore, breathe, and breathe.

644
00:42:30,020 --> 00:42:31,640
It's the rhythm of a waltz.

645
00:42:51,580 --> 00:42:52,420
Huang Yimei,

646
00:42:56,990 --> 00:42:57,970
let's break up.

